name: Happy Christmas Dear Sticky Tape
description:
A unique designer sticky tape to liven up your Christmas wrapping with kissing dears and the caption 'Happy Christmas Dear'

Use this funny tape as a replacement for the usual cellotape or go wild and decorate your presents instead of ribbon! Works well on brown paper too!

Featuring Liz's Christmas Dear from her best selling Christmas Card it is sure to make your recipient smile!

And at a lengthy 66 metres long it is sure to last the Christmas present wrapping marathon!

Buy two rolls for a discount.

Made in the UK.

name: Turkey Apron
description:
Liz's beautifully drawn Turkey screen printed onto a white cotton apron with two pockets.

A great present for a foodie or for those in charge of the Christmas Dinner!

The apron is made from 100% quality cotton and is hand screen printed with our handsome Turkey.

The apron is designed to be very useful in the Kitchen with two front pockets. It is also a large fit 

60cm (w) x 90cm (h)

Matching tea towel available.

Made in the UK and screen printed in Peckham, London.

name: Chase the Rainbow fine bone china Mug
description:
Liz's gorgeous painterly rainbow with the caption "Chase the Rainbow" features on this exquisite fine bone china mug.

The image is screen printed then decorated by hand and fired in Staffordshire.

This fine bone china mug suitable for many occasions to inspire, encourage & wish your recipient the best of luck.

A great gift for those passing exams & graduating this year, but also suitable for anyone that just loves a rainbow.

Made in Britain.
